# DO commit (small CSVs, needed by road module backend):
#   back-end/data/road_model/*.csv           small parameter CSVs
#   back-end/data/multinodeenergy_backend/sector_fuel_codes_to_names*.csv
#
# Do NOT commit (too large or regenerated locally):
#   APEC energy database (>10 MB) — energy-model tab unavailable on HF; startup is graceful
#   Seed workbooks and transport LEAP export workbooks (~130 MB total)
# ===========================
back-end/data/multinodeenergy_backend/00APEC_2024_low_with_subtotals.csv
back-end/data/road_model/*.xlsx
